    "description": "In Lost Soul, you’re a soul that got lost in an unknown place after a plane crash, and now you need to challenge yourself to find your brother!<br><br>You and your brother were planning to take a trip together to go on vacation, but you didn't imagine that the worst could happen…<br><br>Explode the gates using high intensity lasers to open paths and fight enemies, but don't forget to enjoy nature around you :)<br><br>You must face this adventure to save your brother from the evil souls that were on the plane before the crash!<br><br>Do you accept the challenge?<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUSH BOXES TO ACTIVATE TOTEMS!</h2></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182740/extras/2792d1b87aa0f24b9ce7c1bb1faa66cb.avif?t=1703083004\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><strong>Some gates are broken with lasers.</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE THE ENEMIES!</h2></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182740/extras/8d3074101cda7d0de55c197f673dfc00.avif?t=1703083004\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><strong>Don't feel sorry for them, they won't have you.</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT WITH BRAVERY!</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182740/extras/6c7dd8a18027f9c833d1340bb711d72c.avif?t=1703083004\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><strong>Roll to dodge the shots and counter them by attacking at the right moment.</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEWARE OF SOULS!</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182740/extras/318dc1b037329e22930e59eafa8f6dc3.avif?t=1703083004\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><strong>Those are your enemies.</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE PLACE!</h2></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182740/extras/cdae3c75cca9dbdaf29b4eb670c01e9c.avif?t=1703083004\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><strong>Discover new areas.</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARACTERISTICS:</h2></strong> <strong>-Cartoon graphics</strong><br><strong>-Fluid combat</strong><br><strong>-Contains history</strong><br><strong>-Puzzles</strong><br><strong>-Top-down Camera</strong>",
